<a href="http://php.net/manual/en/function.apc-add.php">http://php.net/manual/en/function.apc-add.php</a></p>

<p>Redis: SETNX
<a href="http://code.google.com/p/redis/wiki/SetnxCommand">http://code.google.com/p/redis/wiki/SetnxCommand</a></p>

<p>Memcache: add
